name: Baby Lucifer
description:
Mechanical Baby Lucifer.
Wind up device plays jesus loves me.
Baby spins slowly while the song plays.

Baby Gown is hand sewn and made of red and black felt. Black silk is sewn into the sides, and a black silk hood cover his little head. Over the hood is a sheath of black sparkly tulle. Faces and goat feet are hand sculpted with polymer clay.

Size:
10 inches long
6 inches wide
4 inches thick

More pictures and info here:

Copy & Paste this -> 
http://embryblue.wordpress.com/2013/10/12/how-to-demonize-a-baby-a-walk-on-the-fun-side-of-fall/

name: Haunted Baby Doll Choker
description:
2" x 1.5" Baby Doll Face - sculpt & mold. Each face is hand painted and sealed.



I absolutely love the spooky faces of baby dolls from the Victorian era. I had to recreate one. From an original sculpt, I've made a mold and cast the face. Each face is meticulously hand painted and sealed with a matte acrylic spray. Very lightweight and comfortable. This choker goes well with everyday wear or stunning with Victorian wear.

Package safe for travel, with registered mail.
